**Summary**: DoS via TOML documents with thousands of consecutive commented lines (stack overflow from recursion).

**Dependency chain**: `astro` → `smol-toml@1.6.0` and `@astrojs/markdown-remark` → `smol-toml@1.6.0` (both transitive, in the docs sub-project).

## Fix

Add a pnpm override in `docs/package.json` to force `smol-toml@^1.6.1`, matching the existing pattern for other overrides (`h3`, `devalue`, `rollup`, `svgo`):

### Files Modified

- **`docs/package.json`** — add `"smol-toml": "^1.6.1"` to `pnpm.overrides`
- **`docs/pnpm-lock.yaml`** — regenerated via `cd docs && pnpm install`

